Global Arts and Crafts Tools Market Insights
Arts and Crafts Tools Market size was valued at USD 20.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 32.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Arts and Crafts Tools Market Overview
The global Arts and Crafts Tools market was valued at USD 42.3 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 4.8% during the forecast period (2025-2030). The increasing demand for personalized, hand-crafted goods and the rise of hobby-based activities contribute to market growth. The tools market is driven by consumer interest in DIY projects, as well as a growing number of art and craft enthusiasts globally. Various regions, particularly North America, Europe, and Asia Pacific, are leading the demand for arts and crafts tools, contributing significantly to the market value.

